="text-center mb-6"><div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3" style="background-color:#D97757;"><span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">AI</span></div><h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">创建账户</h2><p class="text-sm text-gray-600">注册并开始使用我们的服务</p></div><form class="space-y-4"><div><label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1.5"> 用户名 </label><input id="name" value="" type="text" required class="w-full px-3 py-2.5 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:border-transparent transition-all" style="--focus-ring-color:#D97757;" onfocus="this.style.borderColor=&#39;transparent&#39;; this.style.boxShadow=&#39;0 0 0 2px #D97757&#39;;" onblur="this.style.borderColor=&#39;#D1D5DB&#39;; this.style.boxShadow=&#39;&#39;;" placeholder="请输入您的用户名"></div><div><label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1.5"> 邮箱地址 </label><input id="email" value="" type="email" required class="w-full px-3 py-2.5 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:border-transparent transition-all" style="--focus-ring-color:#D97757;" onfocus="this.style.borderColor=&#39;transparent&#39;; this.style.boxShadow=&#39;0 0 0 2px #D97757&#39;;" onblur="this.style.borderColor=&#39;#D1D5DB&#39;; this.style.boxShadow=&#39;&#39;;" placeholder="请输入邮箱地址"></div><div><label for="password" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1.5"> 密码 </label><div class="relative"><input id="password" value="" type="password" required class="w-full px-3 py-2.5 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:border-transparent transition-all pr-10" style="--focus-ring-color:#D97757;" onfocus="this.style.borderColor=&#39;transparent&#39;; this.style.boxShadow=&#39;0 0 0 2px #D97757&#39;;" onblur="this.style.borderColor=&#39;#D1D5DB&#39;; this.style.boxShadow=&#39;&#39;;" placeholder="请输入密码"><button type="button" class="absolute inset-y-0 right-0 pr-3 flex items-center"><svg class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.875 18.825A10.05 10.05 0 0112 19c-4.478 0-8.268-2.943-9.543-7a9.97 9.97 0 011.563-3.029m5.858.908a3 3 0 114.243 4.243M9.878 9.878l4.242 4.242M9.878 9.878L3 3m6.878 6.878L21 21"></path></svg></button></div><div class="mt-1.5"><div class="text-xs text-gray-500"><div class="flex items-center space-x-2"><div class="bg-gray-300 w-2 h-2 rounded-full"></div><span>至少8个字符</span></div></div></div></div><div><label for="confirmPassword" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1.5"> 确认密码 </label><input id="confirmPassword" value="" type="password" required class="w-full px-3 py-2.5 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:border-transparent transition-all" style="--focus-ring-color:#D97757;" onfocus="this.style.borderColor=&#39;transparent&#39;; this.style.boxShadow=&#39;0 0 0 2px #D97757&#39;;" onblur="this.style.borderColor=&#39;#D1D5DB&#39;; this.style.boxShadow=&#39;&#39;;" placeholder="请再次输入密码"><!----></div><!----><button type="submit" disabled class="w-full flex justify-center py-2.5 px-4 border border-transparent rounded-lg shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-white hover:shadow-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed transition-all" style="background-color:#D97757;" onmouseover="if(!this.disabled) this.style.backgroundColor=&#39;rgba(217, 119, 87, 0.9)&#39;" onmouseout="if(!this.disabled) this.style.backgroundColor=&#39;#D97757&#39;" onfocus="this.style.boxShadow=&#39;0 0 0 2px #D97757&#39;" onblur="this.style.boxShadow=&#39;&#39;"><!----> 创建账户</button></form><!----><div class="mt-5"><div class="relative"><div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center"><div class="w-full border-t border-gray-300"></div></div><div class="relative flex justify-center text-sm"><span class="px-2 bg-white text-gray-500">已有账户？</span></div></div><div class="mt-4 text-center"><a href